EMBER2024 - Low-End Device Fork
================================

This product is based on EMBER2024 (https://github.com/FutureComputing4AI/EMBER2024).

Original Authors:
    Robert J. Joyce, Gideon Miller, Phil Roth, Richard Zak,
    Elliott Zaresky-Williams, Hyrum Anderson, Edward Raff, James Holt

Reference:
    Joyce et al., "EMBER2024 - A Benchmark Dataset for Holistic Evaluation
    of Malware Classifiers", KDD 2025. https://arxiv.org/pdf/2506.05074

Modifications by:
    M Saadullah Zafar, 2026
    - model.py: refactored for low-end device and batch processing compatibility
    - features.py: updated for signify 0.9.2 API compatibility
    - pyproject.toml: dependencies pinned to exact tested versions, Python >=3.12.10
    - setup.cfg: synced with pyproject.toml; corrected name, version, and
      python_requires; removed build-time packages from install_requires
    See CHANGES.md for full technical details.